{"arkId":"cl010346838","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010346838","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"relief architectural","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"relief architectural"},{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Bas relief : Jupiter enfant et les corybantes"}],"displayDateCreated":"","currentLocation":"Lyon (France), Mus\u00e9e des Beaux-Arts","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"X.483-100","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Relief dit \u0022Plaque Campana\u0022. Sous une frise de 4 palmettes et demi, haute de 14 cm et recourb\u00e9e vers l\u0027avant, Jupiter b\u00e9b\u00e9 est repr\u00e9sent\u00e9 dans les bras d\u0027une femme (Ga\u00efa ou une nymphe?). Ils sont abrit\u00e9s par deux corybantes de profil, coiff\u00e9s de casques corinthiens \u00e0 cimiers, frappant leurs boucliers en dansant hiss\u00e9s sur la pointe des pieds. La femme et l\u0027enfant se regardent. Jupiter touche le sein gauche de son bras gauche. La femme est assise de face, v\u00eatue d\u0027un chit\u00f4n et d\u0027un p\u00e9plos remont\u00e9 sur les genoux. Drap\u00e9s mani\u00e9ristes ; pour les corybantes : plis sinueux.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"76","displayDimension":"76 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"55","displayDimension":"55 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"8,5","displayDimension":"8,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":7,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau